One Achor Clinton Chris has reportedly committed suicide inside his apartment in Rumuekini community, Obio-Akpor Local Government Area of Rivers State. The remains of Chris, who hailed from Rumuokwuta community was found beside a bottle of a brand of Dichlorvos, Sniper inside his apartment in Rumuekini where he resides. Chris’s body was recovered by neighbors who alerted his family members and the Choba Police Division after discovering that the victim who went to bed never saw the light of day. Those who evacuated the remains said he left no note or traces of his action. The incident has been reported to the police who are yet to react. Download Daily Post App.    Subscribe to Daily Post Newsletter.    Advertise with us.   Send us enquiries, press releases.